Make sure to install the `country-flag-icons` package:

```bash
npm install country-flag-icons
```

Choose whichever implementation you prefer - the first one uses Unicode emoji flags, while the second uses SVG flags from the CSS provided by the package. The SVG flags will look more consistent across different platforms.

